Welcome to the API list of Fatina. (Tween, Sequence, Easing)
Fatina  Init(): void This method has to be called once to initialize fatina Pause() / Resume(): void Update(dt: number): void SetTimescale(scale: number): void Tween(obj, properties): Tween Sequence(): Sequence  See MoreFor normal usage
// Initialize Fatina (need to do that only once) Fatina.Init(); // Create a tween to move an object during 250 ms.

 Installation Download the library and include it in your code:
&lt;script src=&quot;fatina.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;   ``` -- More advanced users might want to&hellip; Use npm npm install Fatina  Then include the Fatina module with the standard node.js require:
var Fatina = require('Fatina');  And you can use Fatina as in all other samples :
var t = new Fatina.Tween( /* etc */ ); t.start();
